2:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿MISS想問下「啲」定「尐」先啱？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都要問<br />\n後者都唔知乜撚野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg&h=c9b6b794&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2aeabb9f3486d86ec2c46bd174300ef6def62c27","tid":337414,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:07:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddbae7c3f11666e6c00ba1cd856e2c780e546dd8","tid":337414,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿MISS想問下「啲」定「尐」先啱？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都要問<br />\n後者都唔知乜撚野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg&h=c9b6b794&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n近年有人將「尐」呢個生僻字，講成係「啲」嘅本字或正字，原因係「尐」解作少，同「啲」（解作一點、一些）有相似嘅地方，更有專欄作家同報章評論員將佢誤傳。「啲」嘅讀音係di1，但「尐」嘅讀音係zit3，尐嘅反切係「子列切」，反切上字取聲母(子-&gt;zi-&gt;z)，下字取韻母(列-&gt;lit-&gt;it)，切出嚟嘅音就係zit，讀音都唔啱，所以無可能係本字或正字。而且意思唔係相同，例如「多啲」（多一點），如果寫成「多尐」就會變成（多少），意思已經唔同咗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/尐\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%B0%90&d=jJesrG7db7hc%2F08bn%2FGEQP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=022cd260\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/尐</a></blockquote><br />\n「尐」字好多人用㗎, 包括熱狗, 到時又咩約定俗成啄鳩住你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9911af53c8b408ac4ee8076f71fc5a9389d0e7aa","tid":337414,"uid":404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿MISS想問下「啲」定「尐」先啱？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都要問<br />\n後者都唔知乜撚野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg&h=c9b6b794&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好柒呀 彭志銘亂鳩嚟架 唔係話想撐個肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6839d7dbd55e0b5cf61d9a3a6f492cab045320","tid":337414,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿MISS想問下「啲」定「尐」先啱？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都要問<br />\n後者都唔知乜撚野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F200502_c450a10bb41f93224995b9f2b03e9607.jpg&h=c9b6b794&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好柒呀 彭志銘亂鳩嚟架 唔係話想撐個肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔好咁講呀, 見過人拗十版八版㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc8086dd9707a551aab72788e24fa719e70ac77","tid":337414,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ching Ho ball<br />\n將正字撚趕出連登</blockquote><br />\n矛錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n禾聚討厭正字燃</blockquote><br />\n禾你老母塊閪咩柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}